column1: # Genotype data for F8 filial generation of B6 x D2 mouse advanced
# intercross line. This table includes genotype data for 425 mice
# derived from the C57BL/6J ("B6") and DBA/2J ("D2") inbred strains.
# The table is stored in comma-delimited ("csv") format. Each row
# first two) corresponds to a SNP. Genotypes are either AA
# BB. Missing genotypes are marked as NA (for "not available"). The A
# allele is inherited from B6 inbred strain
# inherited from a D2 strain. All SNP information and genomic
# positions are based on Mouse Genome Assembly 37 from the NCBI
